hoverText.en_US: No higher place to stand on?

text.en_US: Even if a switch is a full level of elevation higher than you...
A normal ledge jump will give you enough height to slash it from below.
Perform a long jump then slash when you reach the box.
Since you slash to do a long jump in the first place...
You can use that slash to hit a switch as you are long jumping!
This jump needs two dashes to be chained as well.
